{"tid":828945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撳錢要小心！櫃員機鍵盤疑被放釘","createTime":"2018-09-20T05:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T05:43:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dad40db75e010cd68d52ab5afcef3c65e8e1a2fb","tid":828945,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180920/_2018092012440719434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180920%2F_2018092012440719434.jpg&h=327429e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼巴士被插針後，櫃員機亦疑被放釘！WhatsApp群組瘋傳一張圖片，可見櫃員機鍵盤上的「輸入」按鈕邊緣被放了兩根短幼釘，但圖片未有提及櫃員機屬哪間銀行及位置。有網民其後在facebook群組「西環變幻時」轉載，提醒網民撳錢時要小心。<br />\n不少網民都大呼危險，直斥放釘者變態，有網民懷疑是釘書釘，「應該刻意放落去，用過嘅釘唔會咁直」，另有網民呼籲大家發現有釘應立即報警。<br />\n撇除櫃員機放釘事件，多間巴士公司自今年中起，遭「刺客」在巴士座椅上插針，有乘客臀部或大腿遭插針刺傷，令人心惶惶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/822262-香港-撳錢要小心！櫃員機鍵盤疑被放釘\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F822262-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%92%B3%E9%8C%A2%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%81%E6%AB%83%E5%93%A1%E6%A9%9F%E9%8D%B5%E7%9B%A4%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%94%BE%E9%87%98&d=hLOWhBhG0hlTLctC6GWcNePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=e35e27fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F822262-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%92%B3%E9%8C%A2%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%81%E6%AB%83%E5%93%A1%E6%A9%9F%E9%8D%B5%E7%9B%A4%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%94%BE%E9%87%98&h=cb652add\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/822262-香港-撳錢要小心！櫃員機鍵盤疑被放釘</a>"},{"pid":"3e8e46c513ff20d1b45d86c1fd6bfc1a0e031766","tid":828945,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:23:45.000Z","msg":"遲下可能有愛滋針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e821a4ff15f74bb58fd6a2b370cc6f